Trap of Ghost Moths''[[Naruto Mobile]]'' |jutsu classification=Genjutsu |jutsu type=Yin Release |jutsu class type=Supplementary |jutsu range=Long |users=Fuen |boruto=No |debut anime=67 |debut shippuden=Yes |boruto anime=No |jutsu media=Anime }} Fuen first uses [[poison]] that is thin and tiny enough to be taken in the air. Her target will inhale the poison and start to see the things that Fuen chooses, like caves, moths, or allies of the target trying to kill the target. When her target is imprisoned in her genjutsu, Fuen charges and kills her target. == Trivia == * Although this technique does not appear directly in the game, it is described in [[Fuen]]'s profile in ''[[Naruto Mobile]]'', where it is called '''Trap of Ghost Moths'''. == References == [[es:Genjutsu: Polillas Venenosas]] [[pl:Technika Iluzji Trującej Ćmy]]
